description._content: Original Collection: Robert W. Henderson Photographic Collection (P 98) Item Number: P098 Slide 03266 Image Description: Thomas W. Thompson served as an extension agent in Sherman, Wasco, and Umatilla County. Thompson was involved with the Extension Service for 30 years and retired in 1977.
